	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Earthshattering Kaboom</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_HELP">
			<Text>Merchants, seeking to exploit the situation surrounding the Barringer Crater, have come seeking your support in their venture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>For the next {4_Turns} nearby Villages generate +2 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture and +2 [ICON_GOLD] Gold, but [ICON_STRENGTH] Crime in the City increases by 10%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Allow a large-scale excavation, for a chance to purchase a massive node of iron ore for {2_InstantYield}!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Allocate {2_InstantYield}, receive {4_GPChange} and a Free Spaceship Factory.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The merchants wish to finance an expedition of researchers to excavate part of the crater in the hope of discovering rare gems and metals.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The volacanic chasms around the crater make journeying across the countryside long and dangerous. The merchants wish to set up trading posts to service the various characters who make their living in the plains.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Having heard a theory, that the crater was created by an enormous iron meteor, the merchants wish to drill deep into the crater to secure the hypothetical motherload. They pledge part of the bounty in exchange for some government funding.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_BARRINGER_CRATER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>The recent validation of Barringer's hypothesis has made the Crater something of an icon in the astronomy community. The entrepreneurs wish to capitalize on this renewed interest and found a private space exploration corp in the vicinity of the crater.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
